{"tid":2408194,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"係度放一堆模型，有冇人會收留？","createTime":"2021-02-14T16:55:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T14:49:43.000Z","uid":373442,"like":1,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"5a8510c7d73bf45c9ea25e636672d617b5984f3f","tid":2408194,"uid":373442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T16:55:00.000Z","msg":"話說，我朋友因土地問題需放棄一堆佢心愛既模型<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢唔捨得就咁送去堆填區，想搵會珍惜佢地既人收留，奈何佢工作太忙冇時間處理，所以我就幫佢手處理。<br />\n<br />\n由於本人對模型一無所知，我只幫手出po，聯絡同交收。<br />\n另外，佢唔希望免費送出，避免有人9排，但亦都唔係要賺啲咩錢。如果有意收留既巴打，<span class=\"red\">我希望每排一隻，捐三十蚊去612或香港拯救貓狗協會</span>，呢個要求應該唔過份？<br />\n<br />\n只能面交，<span class=\"red\">交收地點沙田區，或馬鐵大圍至馬鞍山站</span>，時間再夾<br />\n<br />\n以下係佢既描述：<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">放一箱高達模型 有SD HG MG RG GK改件 ，有個巨大勇者王GK頭像 已上色， 全部已砌，有素組有上色，希望找到真正愛惜佢地嘅同好，數量唔多，全部加埋20零隻左右 </span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WtaMoki.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWtaMoki.jpg&h=f2604c0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如各巴打有興趣亦同意上面紅色字既要求，請留個名，有人想要我先留TG，再影多啲相tg你地揀，依家太夜我唔拆箱了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋模型既野我真係識條鐵，如果你有野想問，我會幫你問佢，但一定要等耐啲先覆到架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家訓先，聽日再覆大家，希望唔好沉，我癈柴P推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6699a5f3082d8e0f4040e925787ea56f8c0d5998","tid":2408194,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T17:01:13.000Z","msg":"勇者王好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da9baf724f1facc91d8e1f2befbae1593c603a5b","tid":2408194,"uid":124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T18:22:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ee4ac4b66d0d7bfeb1227d7779f4f71eea6d25d","tid":2408194,"uid":25260,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T18:28:12.000Z","msg":"逐隻影張相啦<br />\n<br />\n我諗佢都想送俾真心鍾意嘅人"},{"pid":"489b4db06595442fe237a98154ee22fd3ad40434","tid":2408194,"uid":287788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T18:48:47.000Z","msg":"你影好D相 放曬上泥 上左色靚既大把人要"},{"pid":"caa992817d3db29373b35a9d5dd46ffed84f123b","tid":2408194,"uid":335883,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T18:55:49.000Z","msg":"可以幫你keep部份<br />\n等你解決土地問題原封不動比番你"},{"pid":"b558d5c9c290245b97d92ffd2576224e30667fc5","tid":2408194,"uid":87598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T18:59:10.000Z","msg":"有興趣，不過無相好難搞喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60f702874c4e2ba3eb91a475fa28f475c9baa018","tid":2408194,"uid":35711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T19:10:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5035abfaf65f95505d6780a693533d5b7ebf3ee2","tid":2408194,"uid":373119,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T19:19:52.000Z","msg":"勸你小心啲<br />\n舊登送過比人轉手被人賣左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efc679992b0afbeb5899c88e46951556fa39d774","tid":2408194,"uid":16945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T19:27:17.000Z","msg":"留名睇下相都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb76073e0f4639b9501cfd79f65f4487acabd1b4","tid":2408194,"uid":124173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T22:34:43.000Z","msg":"Lm睇高達 自己懶得砌但係又想擺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97314855f8fa1bf545eaee60c5e52bd6b334afea","tid":2408194,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quo